e in its own right in the first half of the 20th century. It has to some extent been influenced by the independently formed combination <i>Jo Anne</i>."],"variants":[{"name":"Johanne","meanings":["and Norwegian feminine form of   Johan ."]},{"name":"Joann","meanings":["From Old French <i>Jo(h)anne</i>, and so a doublet of   Joan .  This too was revived as a given name in its own right in the first half of the 20th century. It has to some extent been influenced by the independently formed combination <i>Jo Anne</i>."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Joane Jordoen was born in July 1411, in Worcester, Worcestershire, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 3 sons with John Caldwell. She died in 1450, in her hometown, at the age of 39."},"et":{"July 1411–1450":"juuli 1411–1450","1409–1450":"1409–1450","1439–Male":"1439–Surnud","1444–1482":"1444–1482","1446–Male":"1446–Surnud","1411–1450":"1411–1450","1446":"1446","1411":"1411","1444":"1444","March 1444":"märts 1444","abt 1439":"umbes 1439","Abt 1446":"umbes 1446","1450":"1450","1482":"1482","1409":"1409","July 1411":"juuli 1411","1439":"1439","Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Worcester, Worcestershire, England":"Worcester, Worcestershire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Toulon-sur-Allier, Allier, Auvergne, France":"Toulon-sur-Allier, Allier, Auvergne, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"July 1411–1450":"heinäkuu 1411–1450","1409–1450":"1409–1450","1439–Male":"1439–Kuollut","1444–1482":"1444–1482","1446–Male":"1446–Kuollut","1411–1450":"1411–1450","1446":"1446","1411":"1411","1444":"1444","March 1444":"maaliskuu 1444","abt 1439":"noin 1439","Abt 1446":"noin 1446","1450":"1450","1482":"1482","1409":"1409","July 1411":"heinäkuu 1411","1439":"1439","Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Worcester, Worcestershire, England":"Worcester, Worcestershire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Toulon-